setAssetOut.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the ASSET_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the caller has the ASSET_ADMIN_ROLE
   ├─ when an auction is live
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when no auctions are live
      ├─ when an auction is live
      │  └─ it should revert
      └─ when no auctions are live
         ├─ when the asset out address is set to the zero address
         │  └─ it should revert
         └─ when the asset out address is not set to the zero address
            ├─ when the asset out is set to the same value as the existing one
            │  └─ it should revert
            └─ when the asset out is set to a different value than the existing one
               ├─ it should set the asset out address
               ├─ it clear the previous asset out params
               └─ it should emit a AssetOutSet event
